T1  - From Contextualizing to Context Theorizing: Assessing Context Effects in Privacy Research
AU  - Xu, Heng
AU  - Zhang, Nan
Y1  - 2022/01/31
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2022/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2021.4249
